## Medical Disclaimer

This software is intended for educational and informational purposes only and should not be used as a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition.

The developers and contributors of this software:
- Make no warranties or representations about the accuracy or completeness of medical information
- Are not responsible for any medical decisions made based on this software
- Recommend always consulting with qualified healthcare professionals
- Emphasize that this tool is meant to assist, not replace, clinical judgment

Use of this software does not establish a doctor-patient relationship.

## HIPAA Compliance Notice

Users of this software are responsible for ensuring their implementation complies with all applicable healthcare regulations, including but not limited to HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act) requirements for handling protected health information (PHI).

The software developers provide this tool as-is and users must implement appropriate safeguards for any patient data according to their local regulations and requirements.
